Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(回顾)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.40,0:00:02.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,JOJO的奇妙冒险 前文回顾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来 和我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.83,0:00:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快滚 我可没叫你来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.64,0:00:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能帮到我？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.11,0:00:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我三年前认识的埃及朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.97,0:00:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿布德尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤炎荒绳！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(620,660)}Red Bind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.04,0:00:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.38,0:00:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我告诉你它的真面目吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那东西既是恶灵 又非恶灵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承太郎 被你当作恶灵的——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.42,0:00:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是以你的生命能量制造出来的 拥有力量的幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.42,0:00:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(1023,660)}Vision
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.02,0:00:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于它会在身边显现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.34,0:00:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此这幻象被命名为——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.73,0:00:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替身！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.73,0:00:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(620,660)}Stand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.35,0:00:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是距今四年前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.63,0:01:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从大西洋近非洲海岸打捞上来的一百年前的棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.49,0:01:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棺材？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.72,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据我回收调查的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.43,0:01:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个棺材是你曾曾祖父 即是我的爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.07,0:01:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔纳森·乔斯达死亡时坐的客船上所载的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.79,0:01:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被发现时里面空无一物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.40,0:01:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我知道里面是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.38,0:01:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和阿布德尔正在追踪那家伙的去向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是邪恶的化身 他的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.68,0:01:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪奥！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是从百年的沉睡中苏醒的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.89,0:01:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而与他战斗 正是我们必须肩负的使命！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.06,0:01:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而在他的后颈上…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这混账家伙头部以下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是我爷爷乔纳森·乔斯达被侵占的肉体啊！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(avant)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:02:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承太郎 等下 等下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.37,0:02:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你落东西了哦 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.78,0:02:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 这是路上小心的吻哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.59,0:02:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这娘们…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再粘着自己的孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯—— 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.22,0:02:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是JoJo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？JoJo？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呀 是JoJo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 JoJo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早啊 JoJo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo 四天没来学校了 都去哪里了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.04,0:02:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我说你 干嘛抱着JoJo的手往上面蹭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.67,0:02:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别套近乎 快走开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 你个丑八怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真烦 搓衣板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1050,710)}丑八怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.91,0:02:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搓衣板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:03:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1050,710)}丑八怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.12,0:03:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搓衣板…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1050,710)}丑八怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搓衣板…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丑八怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1050,710)}搓衣板…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 烦透了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他对我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是对我说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo 等等呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.79,0:03:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.21,0:04:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,树枝！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo跌下楼梯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 他反应过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,树枝撑住了没受什么伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.68,0:04:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是树枝划到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 是掉下来之前划的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会踩空了的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他能召出很强力的替身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪那位大人要派我来收拾他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:05:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我的替身的对手
