Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:46.66,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}鎖のよう連なる 絡み合う宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:46.66,OP_CH,NTP,440,0,0,,{\blur2\an2\fs24}カルマ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:52.88,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}白金で断つ運命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:52.88,OP_CH,NTP,0,200,0,,{\blur2\an2\fs24}ひかり
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:52.88,OP_CH,NTP,200,0,0,,{\blur2\an2\fs24}さだめ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:56.69,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}Stand up! Stand up! Stand up!
