Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:08.34,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}Break you down Break you down Break you down
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.62,0:06:17.23,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}拳放つ 聖なるヴィジョン Stand Proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:23.47,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}百年沉睡的苏醒在召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:30.03,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}星尘遥呼 相继汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:34.90,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}男子汉一行已启程
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:40.53,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}踏上穿越时间的沙漠之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:46.66,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}宿命 如同一串错综连横的枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:52.88,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}挥起白金斩断命运
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:59.93,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}迸射而出的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:06.04,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是高傲的弹头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.62,0:06:17.23,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}铁拳百裂 神圣的幻象 Stand Proud!
